These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, banana, cucumber, papaya
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, soy-milk, iced-tea, coffee
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, emerald, ivory, red
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, golf, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 2. the person eating cucumber is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 3. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 4. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 5. the person eating banana is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 6. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 8. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
10. the person who likes red is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ivory##5
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person eating papaya##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Food          | papaya     | banana   | apple | cucumber |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | tea    | coffee   | iced-tea    |
| Color           | ivory       | red   | emerald   | coral     |
| Sport     | lacrosse       | ice-hockey | weightlifting  | golf      |

