.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, pop, soul, metal
There 4 different types of food: apricot, kale, pumpkin, artichoke
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, goldfish
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, board-games, woodworking, traveling
 1. the person eating pumpkin is on the far right##1
 2. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
 3. the owner of the goldfish is the fan of funk##1
 4. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##5
 5. the fan of soul is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person eating apricot is between the person eating artichoke and the fan of pop##2
 8. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
 9. the owner of the dog is the person eating artichoke##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the right of the fan of pop##5
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Music-Genre      | pop       | funk | metal     | soul     |
| Food   | kale      | apricot       | artichoke | pumpkin |
| Pet           | frog       | goldfish    | dog     | bird         |
| Hobby     | traveling | woodworking     | sudoku     | board-games       |

