The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, fishing, gardening, board-games
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, amaryllis, rose, orchid
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 2. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
 4. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the right of the person who growsorchid##5
 5. the mexican is on the left of the egyptian##1
 6. the person who growsorchid is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
 7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 8. the person who growspoppy is somewhere to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##5
 9. the person who growspoppy is in an even position##4
10. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the egyptian##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who growspoppy##1
12. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
