.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-4::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, artichoke, apricot, grapefruit
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, gardening, chess, baking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, metal, pop, reggae
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, blend, bluemaster, bongani
 1. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5
 2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
 3. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
 4. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person eating apricot##5
 5. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person eating artichoke##5
 6. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the person eating apricot is between the fan of metal and the person eating grapefruit##2
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1
 9. the person eating apricot is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
10. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the right of the person eating artichoke##5
11. the fan of pop is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
12. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the right of the person eating peach##5
13. the fan of metal is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |       3        |      4      |
| Food      | peach | artichoke     | apricot        | grapefruit      |
| Hobby           | gardening    | baking   | chess | reading |
| Music-Genre   | reggae      | metal    | country        | pop         |
| Cigar         | dunhill    | bluemaster | bongani         | blend    |

