House: craftsman, victorian, gothic-revival, wooden
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, october, may, august
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, skateboard, taxi
 1. the videographer is somewhere to the left of the security-guard##5
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the victorian house##1
 3. the videographer is somewhere to the left of the software-developer##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the software-developer##1
 5. the person driving the roller is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5
 6. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
 7. the wooden house is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 8. the craftsman house is somewhere to the left of the software-developer##5
 9. the person driving the taxi is the person who's birthday is in may##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4
11. the social-worker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
12. the victorian house is on the left of the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3       |      4       |
| Job         | videographer | software-developer    | social-worker | security-guard  |
| House   | craftsman  | victorian   | wooden       | gothic-revival |
| Birthday   | july | october        | august       | may      |
| Transport     | roller  | helicopter | skateboard   | taxi         |

