 1. the journalist is between the owner of the fish and the person driving the trike##2
 2. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is in an odd position##4
 4. the software-developer is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
 5. the person driving the trike is the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
 9. the chef is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
10. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
12. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
13. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2      |    3     |     4     |
