 2. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who likes light-blue and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2
 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##5
 5. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5
 6. the fan of salsa is the fan of salsa##1
 7. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
 8. the fan of d&b is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 9. the fan of dubstep is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
10. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the fan of d&b##5
11. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blood-red##5
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4

