 3. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
 4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 5. the person eating radish is the montecristo-smoker##1
 6. the prince-smoker is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person eating apple##2
 7. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
 8. the person eating radish is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3
10. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3
11. the montecristo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapes##5

