.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-18::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, dubstep, soul, country
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, oliveros, bolivar, game
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, red, apricot, pink
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, drama, epic
 1. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the right of the game-smoker##5
 2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 3. the person who likes turquise is between the fan of metal and the person who likes pink##2
 4. the oliveros-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who likes pink##5
 5. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
 6. the fan of country is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
 8. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who likes red##5
 9. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
10. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the fan of soul##1
11. the person watching drama movies is somewhere to the right of the fan of country##5
12. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3      |        4        |
| Music-Genre      | country   | metal | dubstep   | soul          |
| Cigar          | oliveros    | game        | bolivar     | bluemaster          |
| Color           | red | apricot        | turquise | pink |
| Movie-Genre   | epic    | adventure     | drama      | disaster        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, water
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, frog, rat, mouse
House: cottage, art-deco, palace, modern
4 different games are played: whist, snooker, domino, go
 1. the person playing snooker is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
 4. the palace house is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the rat and the modern house##2
 6. the palace house is in an odd position##4
 7. the owner of the rat is the art-deco house##1
 8. the palace house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
 9. the person playing domino is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
10. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing go##1
11. the person playing domino is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person playing go is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
13. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the right of the palace house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | water      | hot-chocolate | coffee     |
| Pet           | mouse   | goldfish  | frog        | rat |
| House   | cottage     | modern     | palace      | art-deco   |
| Game     | snooker | domino | go          | whist     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, blood-red, azure, red
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, mechanic, social-worker, teacher
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, 7up, iced-tea, mirinda
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, chaman, tiparillo, davidoff
 1. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5
 2. the davidoff-smoker is the person who likes blue##1
 3. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the left of the alhambra-smoker##5
 4. the architect is in an even position##4
 5. the mechanic is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
 6. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the right of the chaman-smoker##5
 7. the social-worker is the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the architect##5
 9. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the right of the person who likes azure##5
11. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person who likes red##5
12. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person who likes azure##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Color          | blue | azure  | red    | blood-red       |
| Job           | mechanic  | teacher | social-worker | architect  |
| Beverage   | 7up    | iced-tea   | mirinda  | water     |
| Cigar   | davidoff      | tiparillo    | chaman        | alhambra |

 